<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Geolocation Conversational Assistant</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/favicon.ico">
  <style>
    :root {
      color-scheme: dark;
      --bg: #1a102a;
      --text: #eaeaea;
      --accent: #6b5b95;
      --hover: #bca9ff;
      --font: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }
    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: var(--font);
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
      max-width: 500px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0 20px 40px;
      color: #cfcfcf;
    }
    .buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text);
      background: var(--accent);
      padding: 12px 24px;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    a:hover {
      background: var(--hover);
      color: #111;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Geolocation Conversational Assistant</h1>
  <p>
    An interactive conversational assistant. Just a little fun project!
  </p>
